high_descs: Turn left and walk forward to the bath tub.
Pick up the bar of soap from the bath tub basin.
Turn around and walk forward to the sink on the left.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the bath tub.
Put the bar of soap back into the bath tub basin, to the left of the black cloth.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned bar of soap in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn to your left and go to the bathtub across from you.
Pick up the bar of soap in the bath tub, to the right of the rag.
Turn around and go to the first sink on your left.
Put the bar of soap in the sink, turn the water on, rinse the soap off, turn the water off, and take the bar of soap out of the sink.
Turn to your left and go back to the bathtub.
Place the bar of soap back in the bathtub, to the left of the rag.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap in the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn left and move to the bathtub.
Pick up the pink bar of soap to the right of the gray rag from the bathtub.
Turn right and move the sink closest to the bathtub.
Place the bar of soap in the sink, rinse it with water from the faucet, then pick up the bar of soap.
Turn left and move to the left edge of the bathtub .
Place the bar of soap to the left of the gray rag in the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean bar of soap in the bathtub.
